.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-6::.
There 4 different types of food: broccoli, pineapple, corn, garlic
The people have 4 different hobbies: video-games, sudoku, singing, reading
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, climbing, weightlifting, sailing
1. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left of the person who's sport is climbing##1
2. the person eating broccoli is on the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
3. the person eating broccoli is on the right of the person who's sport is cricket##1
4. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left of the person eating pineapple##1
5. the person who's hobby is video-games is between the person who's hobby is reading and the person who's sport is weightlifting##2
6. the person eating pineapple is between the person eating broccoli and the person eating corn##2
7. the person who's sport is cricket is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |   3    |     4      |
| Food    | corn | pineapple  | broccoli | garlic      |
| Hobby   | singing  | reading  | video-games | sudoku |
| Sport   | sailing | cricket | climbing | weightlifting     |

