.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-7::.
There 4 different types of food: pumpkin, cabbage, carrot, cherry
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: superhero, action, thriller, crime
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: sailing, basketball, skateboarding, rowing
1. the person who's sport is rowing is the person watching action movies##1
2. the person who's sport is skateboarding is the person watching superhero movies##1
3. the person watching thriller movies is on the far left##1
4. the person watching crime movies is on the right of the person watching thriller movies##1
5. the person eating carrot is on the left of the person who's sport is sailing##1
6. the person eating cabbage is between the person watching action movies and the person watching thriller movies##2
7. the person eating cherry is on the left of the person watching superhero movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Food          | carrot  | cabbage    | cherry | pumpkin  |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller | crime       | action        | superhero    |
| Sport         | basketball | sailing | rowing  | skateboarding |

