.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-8::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: rock-climbing, filmmaking, gardening, writing
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: sports, superhero, animation, horror
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, turtle, bird, pony
1. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the owner of the chinchilla##1
2. the person watching superhero movies is between the owner of the pony and the person who's hobby is filmmaking##2
3. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the right of the owner of the bird##1
4. the owner of the bird is on the right of the owner of the chinchilla##1
5. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the person who's hobby is writing##1
6. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left of the person watching animation movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3    |      4      |
| Hobby         | writing  | filmmaking | gardening | rock-climbing |
| Movie-Genre   | sports  | horror | superhero   | animation         |
| Pet           | chinchilla | bird  | turtle   | pony      |

