.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-9::.
There 4 different types of food: pomegranate, potato, broccoli, nectarine
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, traveling, puzzles, baking
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: dubstep, hip-hop, trance, blues
1. the fan of trance is on the left of the fan of blues##1
2. the person who's hobby is traveling is the person eating pomegranate##1
3. the fan of hip-hop is on the left of the person eating potato##1
4. the person who's hobby is puzzles is the person eating potato##1
5. the person eating pomegranate is on the right of the person eating nectarine##1
6. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the far right##1
7. the person who's hobby is traveling is between the fan of trance and the person who's hobby is card-games##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3    |      4      |
| Food          | nectarine  | pomegranate    | broccoli | potato       |
| Hobby         | baking | traveling | card-games  | puzzles |
| Music-Genre   | trance   | blues      | hip-hop  | dubstep     |

