The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, reading, filmmaking, cooking
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: martial-arts, satire, spy, crime
1. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the far left##1
2. the person eating carrot is on the far left##1
3. the person eating apricot is between the person eating watermelon and the person who's hobby is reading##2
4. the person watching satire movies is on the right of the person eating artichoke##1
5. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the far right##1
6. the person watching satire movies is on the right of the person eating artichoke##1
7. the person watching crime movies is the person who's hobby is cooking##1
8. the person watching martial-arts movies is the person eating artichoke##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |   3    |    4    |
