.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-11::.
There 4 different types of food: pomegranate, tomato, artichoke, papaya
The people have 4 different hobbies: chess, magic-tricks, card-games, baking
4 different pets are kept: hedgehog, horse, turtle, snake
1. the person eating tomato is on the right of the person eating pomegranate##1
2. the owner of the turtle is the person eating tomato##1
3. the owner of the hedgehog is between the person who's hobby is magic-tricks and the person who's hobby is card-games##2
4. the person who's hobby is card-games is between the owner of the hedgehog and the person eating papaya##2
5. the person who's hobby is card-games is the owner of the snake##1
6. the person who's hobby is chess is the owner of the horse##1
7. the person who's hobby is baking is the owner of the hedgehog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |    3     |     4      |
| Food    | papaya  | artichoke | pomegranate | tomato     |
| Hobby   | chess | card-games   | baking  | magic-tricks    |
| Pet     | horse        | snake       | hedgehog      | turtle |

