.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-12::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, milk, fanta, coffee
The people have 4 different hobbies: rock-climbing, photography, woodworking, singing
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, rabbit, ferret, rat
1. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
2. the person who's hobby is singing is the person drinking fanta##1
3. the person drinking milk is between the person drinking fanta and the person who's hobby is photography##2
4. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the far left##1
5. the person drinking milk is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1
6. the owner of the chinchilla is on the far right##1
7. the owner of the ferret is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2     |      3      |     4     |
| Beverage   | coffee | fanta     | milk | cola       |
| Hobby      | woodworking  | singing | rock-climbing  | photography |
| Pet        | rat  | rabbit      | ferret        | chinchilla      |

