3. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
4. the person drinking lemonade is the owner of the rat##1
5. the owner of the bird is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
6. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the person who's hobby is dancing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2    |     3      |    4    |
| Beverage   | lemonade | hot-chocolate  | tea       | iced-tea   |
| Hobby      | traveling     | dancing | woodworking | skydiving |
| Pet        | rat        | fish | hedgehog     | bird |

