.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-14::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  bartender, dressmaker, software-developer, architect
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: comedy, horror, thriller, musical
The people use 4 different means of transport: tram, motorbike, van, taxi
1. the person watching comedy movies is the person driving the taxi##1
2. the person driving the van is the software-developer##1
3. the person driving the van is on the left of the bartender##1
4. the person watching musical movies is on the left of the person driving the taxi##1
5. the person driving the motorbike is between the person watching thriller movies and the software-developer##2
6. the person driving the taxi is on the far right##1
7. the person driving the motorbike is the architect##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Job           | dressmaker | architect | software-developer    | bartender   |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller      | horror   | musical | comedy |
| Transport     | tram     | motorbike       | van        | taxi    |

