The people prefer 4 different music-genres: techno, blues, disco, ambient
There are 4 different nationalities: colombian, french, thai, canadian
1. the fan of techno is the person drinking 7up##1
2. the person drinking coffee is between the person drinking fanta and the french##2
3. the person drinking fanta is the fan of blues##1
4. the person drinking fanta is between the fan of disco and the canadian##2
5. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
6. the colombian is between the thai and the fan of ambient##2
7. the fan of techno is the canadian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |    4     |
