.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-17::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: water, 7up, hot-chocolate, cola
There 4 different types of food: asparagus, strawberry, plum, watermelon
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, lacrosse, skateboarding, climbing
1. the person drinking water is on the far left##1
2. the person eating plum is between the person drinking cola and the person who's sport is skateboarding##2
3. the person who's sport is climbing is on the right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
4. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the far right##1
5. the person eating asparagus is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
6. the person eating strawberry is on the right of the person eating plum##1
7. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the person who's sport is biathlon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |    2    |       3       |    4     |
| Beverage   | water    | 7up | cola           | hot-chocolate |
| Food       | asparagus | plum    | strawberry          | watermelon   |
| Sport      | skateboarding  | lacrosse   | climbing | biathlon  |

