4. the person drinking almond-milk is between the person watching satire movies and the person watching thriller movies##2
5. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
6. the owner of the ferret is between the person drinking fanta and the owner of the pony##2
7. the person watching crime movies is the owner of the ferret##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2       |    3     |   4   |
| Beverage      | coffee | almond-milk | fanta     | iced-tea   |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller | crime        | satire  | family  |
| Pet           | pony      | ferret         | chinchilla | rat |

