3. the videographer is on the far left##1
4. the person driving the car is the paramedic##1
5. the person who's sport is parkour is the person driving the car##1
6. the person driving the airplane is between the person who's sport is sailing and the person driving the car##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2      |     3      |      4       |
| Job         | videographer        | paramedic  | designer | security-guard   |
| Sport       | cycling | parkour | skiing    | sailing |
| Transport   | ship        | car     | airplane       | bike      |

