.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-20::.
There 4 different types of food: eggplant, lettuce, radish, zucchini
4 different pets are kept: rabbit, turtle, horse, rat
The people use 4 different means of transport: roller, boat, subway, train
1. the owner of the rabbit is on the far left##1
2. the person eating eggplant is on the right of the owner of the turtle##1
3. the person driving the boat is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1
4. the person eating radish is on the far right##1
5. the person driving the train is the owner of the rat##1
6. the owner of the turtle is between the person eating zucchini and the person driving the subway##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Food        | zucchini | lettuce | eggplant | radish |
| Pet         | rabbit       | turtle     | horse   | rat   |
| Transport   | roller | boat | subway | train |

 